text: Jordyn Poulter (born 31 July 1997) is an American volleyball player. She was a member of the United States women's national volleyball team. She played at the 2013 FIVB Volleyball Girls' U18 World Championship, 2018 Women's Pan- American Volleyball Cup, 2019 FIVB Volleyball Women's Nations League. She played for the University of Illinois's women's volleyball team. == References == Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:American volleyball players
